title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada - Hatley Park National Historic Site
description:
In this video we will fly over Hatley Park National Historic Site. Hatley Park National Historic Site is located in Colwood, British Columbia, in Greater Victoria. It is the site of Hatley Castle, a Classified Federal Heritage Building. Since 1995, the mansion and estate have been used for the public Royal Roads University. From the 1940s to 1995, it was used for the Royal Roads Military College, a naval training facility
